des:
Use all Alexa facilities to switch on, off, control the intensity, change the colors of your Lamp and to use the features of Elsys smart devices. Just talk to Alexa!

To enjoy, it will be necessary to connect Alexa to your Elsys products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Elsys Casa+" app in Google Play or AppStore; 
(2) Register your account; 
(3) You will need to have some Elsys smart devices in hand; 
(4) Configure these devices in app Elsys Casa+ and give names to them; 
(5) Download Amazon Alexa app in app store; 
(6) Configure your device Alexa on app; 
(7) Search "Elsys Casa+" in Skill tab on Alexa app; 
(8) Click to enable the Skill "Elsys Casa+", and you'll be navigated to the login page; 
(9) Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking; 
(10) Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these: 
"Alexa, turn on kitchen light" 
"Alexa, turn off kitchen light" 
"Alexa, dim livingroom light" 
"Alexa, brighten living room light" 
"Alexa, set the living room light to 20 percent"
"Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
“Alexa, turn on the switch”
“Alexa, turn off the switch”
